@startuml repository_class_step01
title LeSonStore — Bước 1: Repository Pattern (orderRepository)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Controller Layer" {
  class "orderController.js" as OrderCtrl <<controller>> {
    +createOrder(req, res, next)
    +cancelOrder(req, res, next)
  }
}

package "Repository Layer\nserver/services/order/" {
  class "orderRepository.js" as OrderRepo <<repository>> {
    +reserveVariationStock(variationId, quantity, transaction)
    +createPaymentRecord(data, transaction)
    +findOrderWithItemsAndPayment(orderId, { userId, transaction, lockOrder })
    +releaseVariationStock(variationId, quantity, transaction)
  }
}

package "Model Layer (Sequelize)\nserver/models/" {
  class Order <<entity>> {
    +order_id
    +user_id
    +status
    +findOne(options)
  }

  class OrderItem <<entity>> {
    +order_id
    +variation_id
    +quantity
    +findAll(options)
  }

  class Payment <<entity>> {
    +order_id
    +provider
    +payment_status
    +create(data, options)
    +findOne(options)
  }

  class ProductVariation <<entity>> {
    +variation_id
    +stock_quantity
    +findOne(options)
    +decrement(field, options)
    +increment(field, options)
  }
}

interface "Transaction\n(sequelize.transaction())" as Txn {
  +commit()
  +rollback()
  +LOCK.UPDATE
}

OrderCtrl --> OrderRepo : gọi trong\ncreateOrder / cancelOrder

OrderRepo --> Order : findOne\n(lockOrder: FOR UPDATE)
OrderRepo --> OrderItem : findAll
OrderRepo --> Payment : create / findOne
OrderRepo --> ProductVariation : findOne + lock\n decrement / increment

OrderRepo ..> Txn : mọi hàm nhận\ntransaction

note right of OrderRepo
  **Repository che Sequelize:**
  Controller không gọi trực tiếp
  ProductVariation.findOne(lock)
  hay Payment.create — logic DB
  tập trung tại orderRepository.js
end note

note bottom of OrderCtrl
  Bước 3 (chưa có): orderFacade
  sẽ orchestration → gọi OrderRepo
  **Không** thay thế Repository
end note

note as N1
  **createOrder** dùng:
  reserveVariationStock
  createPaymentRecord
end note

note as N2
  **cancelOrder** dùng:
  findOrderWithItemsAndPayment
  releaseVariationStock
end note

OrderRepo .. N1
OrderRepo .. N2

@enduml
